		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="438" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩飘浮灵喷出3个弱追踪性的岩弹，移动速度较快，每个造成<span color="#ffe599">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩飘浮灵朝前，旋转扇叶不断朝玩家突进，造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="436" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩飘浮灵死亡。<br/><span color="#f2d899">未满怒：</span><span>直接爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害；<br/></span><span color="#f2d899">满怒：</span><span>蓄力爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">120%</span><span>伤害，范围比其他飘浮灵大得多。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
