			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">&lt;18.75%HP<br/>&gt;18.75%HP<br/>&gt;31.25%HP<br/>&gt;43.75%HP<br/>&gt;56.25%HP</p>
